# Fetch URL to Knowledge Base

Download a web page and add it to the knowledge base.

## Usage

```
/lsearch-fetch <url> [title]
```

## Arguments

- `url` (required): URL to fetch
- `title` (optional): Custom title for the document

## Your task

Fetch the provided URL and add it to the knowledge base.
